cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and speech processing, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.SD (Sound). The use of neural networks for segmentation and translation also suggests a possible categorization under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised learning, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SD.
